<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Anipenda Kweli TZR28</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Anipenda ni kweli;
 Mungu anena hili;
 Sisi wake watoto;
 kutulinda si zito.

[C1]
   Yesu anipenda,
   Yesu anipenda,
   Kweli anipenda,
   Mungu amesema.

[V2]
 Kwa kupenda akafa
 Niokoke na kufa;
 Atazidi taka,
 Sana ataniweka.

[V3]
 Anipenda kabisa;
 Niuguapo sasa
 Anitunza Mbinguni
 Niliyelala chini.

[V4]
 Kunipenda haachi,
 Tu sote hapa chini
 Baada ya mashaka
 Kwake tanipeleka.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>28</hymn_number>
</song>